TO ENTRYPOINT GRAFETE STO DOCKERFILE kai tou leei otan ekinisei to pod ti na ektelesei san entolh 
afto mporei na ginei overrigth mesa apo to deployment me thn entolh command diladi



DOCKERFILE
----------
ENTRYPOINT ["sleep"]
CMD ["5"]

Pod
---
command:["sleep.02"]
args:["5"]

telefteo pianete afto tou pod kai to kanei overwrite afta tou DOCKERFILE



DLD TO command antikathista to ENTRYPOINT kai to args to CMD
command ---> ENTRYPOINT
args    ---> CMD